タンの間を一文字分空けたい。</p>\n<p>送信成功の際のメッセージを囲む枠をデフォルトの緑から任意の色（x）に変え、<br />\n枠内の色も任意の色（x）に変えたい。</p>\n<p>.wpcf7 wpcf7c-conf {<br />\n    background-color: #x;}<br />\n.wpcf7 input.wpcf7c-btn-back {<br />\n    background-color: #x;}<br />\n.wpcf7 input.wpcf7c-btn-back {<br />\n    margin-right: 1em;}<br />\n.wpcf7 wpcf7-mail-sent-ok {<br />\n    background-color: #x;<br />\n    border: 2px solid #x;}</p>\n<p>お手数おかけしますが、どうぞよろしくお願い致します。</p>\n						\n					\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:6:\"nekoco\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:2;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"\n					\n					\n					\n					\n					\n\n					\n\n					\n					\n				\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:2:{s:0:\"\";a:5:{s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:129:\"https://ja.wordpress.org/support/topic/jetpack%e3%81%ae%e5%85%b1%e6%9c%89%e3%80%81twitter%e3%81%ae%e7%94%bb%e5%83%8f/#post-212583\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:46:\"返信先: Jetpackの共有、twitterの画像\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:129:\"https://ja.wordpress.org/support/topic/jetpack%e3%81%ae%e5%85%b1%e6%9c%89%e3%80%81twitter%e3%81%ae%e7%94%bb%e5%83%8f/#post-212583\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Thu, 19 Jan 2017 08:07:46 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"da